      "content": "i honestly dont even know why im still waking up in the morning. everything i spent twenty years building is just... gone. the firm, the reputation, even my own family barely looks at me. i feel like a ghost walking around in a life that doesnt belong to me anymore. there's nothing left to actually be.",
